drm/i915/dsi: add support for DSI PLL N1 divisor values

Currently DSI PLL N1 is hardcoded off. Make it possible to use it
later. This should have no functional changes for now.

v2: s/ffz(~(n))/ffs(n) - 1/ (Ville)

